          "description": "I was visiting from out-of-state and having problems with swelling around a damaged toenail nail on my left big toe. They took my Medicare insurance information and only charged me my minimum copay - just what I would have paid in Houston. The doctor was prompt, friendly and prescribed an antibiotic that almost immediately reduced painful swelling. I highly recommend CityMD.",
