          "description": "Front desk receptionist was great, patient and friendly.\n\nThe nurse who did the check in was also great.\n\nBut whenever I'm told it \"could be this or could be that\" by a doctor, I find that difficult because I've already come up with a list of things it \"could be\" before I arrived. The reason I'm at the doctor's office is to find out what exactly it is.\n\nI wasted my co-pay on my could be diagnosis.",
